<P>
 Hurray to "Lois & Clark: The New Adventures of Superman's" new season of 
episodes (ABC).The writing is filled with action, suspense and romance. The 
scenes are done with beautiful visual effects, such as Superman flying in and 
out of buildings and zigzagging around buildings. Don't forget his X-ray 
