<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102394-0046 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 091246 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 23, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Magazine; Page 32; Magazine Desk 
