<TEXT>
<P>
 To help prevent travelers from getting lost or accidentally straying off main 
roads into high-crime areas in Florida, about 400 signs with bright orange 
sunburst logos are going up in the Miami area to mark highway lanes and exits 
deemed safe for tourists to travel. 
