</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Quarterback Babe Laufenberg, who already had made stops at Stanford and 
Missouri, found a home at Pierce College in 1981.  
</P>
<P>
 The former Crespi High standout passed for 1,590 yards for the Brahmas. 
</P>
<P>
 He went on to play at Indiana and in the NFL. 
