<HEADLINE>
<P>
FUNK CARRIES VILLAGE CHRISTIAN, 15-12 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MATTHEW AVILA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jacob Funk rushed for 183 yards and two touchdowns in 40 carries Saturday, 
leading Village Christian to a 15-12 Alpha League victory over Marshall 
Fundamental. 
</P>
<P>
 Aaron Funk of Village Christian (4-3, 2-0 in league play) intercepted a pass 
early in the fourth quarter that led to a game-winning one-yard touchdown run 
by Jacob Funk. 
</P>
<P>
 Jacob Funk scored on a two-yard run in the second quarter. 
</P>
<P>
 Marshall Fundamental (1-6, 1-1) had a 12-7 halftime lead. Jonathan Chambers 
threw a 12-yard touchdown pass to Shamar Griffin and Patrick Walker returned an 
interception 23 yards for a touchdown. MATTHEW AVILA 
</P>
</TEXT>
