 Eric Wayman and Joe Huang had two goals for Estancia. 
</P>
<P>
 In the semifinals: 
</P>
<P>
 Estancia 9, Laguna Beach (JV) 8 -- Chad Bollenbach scored the winning goal two 
minutes into overtime for Estancia in the semifinal game. Bollenbach, who had 
four goals in the game, also scored the tying goal with 44 seconds left in 
regulation. 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Margarita 20, Pacifica 3 -- Tony Bierenkoven had seven goals to lead 
Santa Margarita (10-9) in a semifinal game. 
</P>
<P>
 In other games: 
</P>
<P>
 Century 14, Magnolia 8 -- Jorge Grijalba scored 10 goals to lead Century 
(10-8) in a consolation game. He also had 17 in a 24-12 victory over Calvary 
Chapel in an earlier game. 
</P>
