 Cypress 17, Garden Grove 8 -- Erik Sandzig had five goals to lead Cypress 
(12-9) in a seventh-place game. Mark Slezcove and David Watkins also had four 
goals for the Centurions. 
</P>
<P>
 Jason Holbrook had five goals for Garden Grove (7-10). 
</P>
<P>
 Fountain Valley 19, Cypress 14 -- Tim Causee scored seven goals to lead 
Fountain Valley (11-9). David Watkins and Erik Sandzig had six goals each for 
Cypress (11-9). 
