<P>
9 KILLED BY TORRENTIAL DOWNPOUR IN GREECE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A three-hour downpour here backed up sewers and caused severe flooding, 
killing nine people, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
 Most of the victims of the heavy rain late Friday were trapped in basement 
apartments in the northern suburbs, police said. 
