 Next week: Eagle Rock at Hollywood; Verdugo Hills at Marshall 
</P>
<P>
 Salesian 21, Pius X 0--Johnny Flores returned the opening kickoff 93 yards for 
a touchdown and Rafael Morales scored on a 52-yard interception return, leading 
the Mustangs to a Santa Fe League win at Roosevelt High. 
</P>
